{"tid":369122,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哈利簡尼：今季必須贏得冠軍","createTime":"2017-08-22T05:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T09:06:38.000Z","uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b39747eff56858c1597f339900c2195fec5449ca","tid":369122,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:20:10.000Z","msg":"據天空體育報導，哈利-簡尼說，今季熱刺必須贏得一項冠軍獎盃，才能讓他們繼續保持上升態勢。<br />\n<br />\n　　上週末，在被車路士擊敗後，簡尼被問到，普捷天奴執教熱刺的第4個賽季，是不是必須要拿到冠軍，簡尼說：「是的，這是我們必須要做到的。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">前兩個賽季分別是第三和第二。我們唯一可以提升的方式，就是贏得一些冠軍，或者是聯賽冠軍。那是我們的目標。</strong></span>那也是我們一直以來的目標。我們必須要保持住，希望這可以發生。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「這是我們在一起工作的又一年。我們更加習慣了這種踢球方式。」"},{"pid":"c72adcf51cc7392fbf5308066601aa9062667b4f","tid":369122,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"第一場就輸左3分"},{"pid":"0d76151bae983f105d6e60e786d411694498cac8","tid":369122,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一場就輸左3分</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/kRQzoj1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkRQzoj1.gif&h=4b50ecac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c95b4bcd7d513a41c1de8b9a717c44c1bad0b05","tid":369122,"uid":45650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:26:43.000Z","msg":"拿拿臨一月轉會曼聯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e9a8d0a6601f5ea1681557d23ddb0636ac7ca3","tid":369122,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一場就輸左3分</blockquote><br />\n[img<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/kRQzoj1.gif[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkRQzoj1.gif%5